{"id":"zimmah","term":"Zimmah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Mischief. (1.) A Gershonite Levite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 6:20\">1 Chr. 6:20</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) Another Gershonite Levite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 6:42\">1 Chr. 6:42</a>).</p>\n<p>(3.) The father of Joah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 29:12\">2 Chr. 29:12</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 6:20","1 Chronicles 6:42","2 Chronicles 29:12"]}